rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard you subdued that rebel faction,
Lindwurm. You know, I'm starting to
think you can do anything!

rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Both Don Dondon and Bahn are under
lock and key, and Senator Stulc's
finally started giving his testimony.

rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I know it's strange coming from me,
but thank you. For everything.

rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0004
rows.name:
You've saved the empire, which
means I'm not out of a job, and
I can still provide for my family!
